data.description: An extraordinary opportunity awaits in highly sought after North Lawndale!  This stunning 2-flat built in 2007 is a true rarity providing modern amenities and a prime location.  The newly remodeled second-floor unit is a sanctuary of luxury and style. This freshly painted living space exudes elegance with an expansive open floor plan, cathedral ceilings, custom wood burning fireplace, 3 generously sized bedrooms, new waterproof laminate flooring throughout, sophisticated and spacious bathroom, sun filled kitchen with gleaming stainless-steel appliances, generous counter space with stylish island, in unit laundry room with washer/dryer included.  The 1st floor unit is occupied with a month-to-month tenant in place.  This unit features a seamless open concept living area with spacious island and modern appliances, large laundry room with W/D hookup, waterproof laminate flooring, 3 generously sized bedrooms with cozy carpet & wall-to-wall closets in the master bedroom.  The property reveals a private backyard oasis enclosed by a privacy fence, creating a perfect retreat for outdoor gatherings and relaxation. Additionally, this gem includes a 2-car garage, ensuring convenient parking and extra storage space, a coveted feature in city living.    This property presents an unparalleled opportunity for investors and homeowners alike(3 minutes from projected $68 million INVEST South/West Innovation center project and only 10 minutes from downtown).  Don't miss your chance to own this exceptional property.   Schedule a viewing today!
